Commentary: |
  The function of an Avatar is universal and non-limitative in scope. Thus,
  the parables of Christ are for each to understand according to his capacity.
---
Dhamma has been taught by me without making a distinction between esoteric
and exoteric. For the Tathagata has not the closed fist of a teacher in
respect of mental states.
